name: The 7 Talisman of Work: Mallet
description:
A swipe with this mean bastard of a tool would render you useless.
Yet it's not a mallet for beating humanity.
It's a giant of opportunity.
A free pass to the next world.
It has the capacity to incapacitate.
It's has the ability to make unable.
But it's only for the gentlest and warmest heart.
The holder is the King and Queen of the Universe. 
Without it, no true soul may feel complete.
